  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13096244/star_arctic_igloos_-2-1.jpg" alt="LaplandAccommodationOptions" data-udi="umb://media/a269e1f182cb4307a0b8564118b3b720" /></p>
<p>Inghams <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland holidays</a> are truly magical from the moment you arrive in Finland. We offer over 30 accommodation options across our 3 resorts in Lapland - <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselka</a>, ensuring there is the perfect place to stay for your needs.</p>
<p>No matter your requirements, we have the ideal accommodation for you - choose from Hotels, Apartments, Cabins &amp; Lodges.</p>
<p><strong>Hotels</strong> - The perfect options when you want to a relaxing stay, with in-house catering, hotel assistance when needed and on-site spas.</p>
<p><strong>Apartments</strong> - Ideal for making the holiday your own, enjoy the space an apartment offers and enjoy making breakfast at your own leisure.</p>
<p><strong>Cabins &amp; Lodges</strong> - A must stay if you are looking to emerge yourself in Lapland life and live like a local in beautiful, traditional cabins, lodges and cottages.</p>]]></bodyText>
